description:
Gabriel has a rather unusual occupation. He works for a company that builds custom limos out of regular vehicles. It's scary how much he knows about cars!
He's got a great muscular body and a cute smile, so you'd think he was a player. However, it's just the opposite — he's very, very shy and, as he tells it, somewhat intimidated by beautiful women. He's dating a girl that a co-worker set him up with, but it's nothing serious yet.
Gabriel is a shooter. One of his cumshots shoots straight up in the air and goes clear over his head!
title: Gabriel
